Admin :

1 - He should be able to login 
2 - crud teacher 
3 - crud student 
4 - crud session between teacher and student
5 - approve/reject the status of a session 
6 - change the payement status 

Session 
{
    id : string
    teacher : Teacher_id (FK)
    student : Student_id (FK)  // every session has one student , every student has one or many sessions
    done : bool
    paid : bool
}
Teacher {
    id : string 
    name : string
    password : string
}

Student
{
    id 
    username : string
    sessions : session_id (FK)
}

Payement
{
    id 
    amount:float
    date: date
    to : Teacher_id (FK)
    done : bool
}

Admin
{
    id : string
    username/nickname : string 
    photo_url : string 
    password : string
    transactions : total (num of rows in payement)
    currrency : string 
}
